============================================================
FRONTEND ENV REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create:

frontend/.env.example

With:

VITE_APP_NAME=zDash
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
VITE_ENABLE_MOCK_FALLBACK=true
VITE_POLL_INTERVAL_MS=5000
VITE_DEFAULT_THEME=dark
VITE_SHOW_SAFETY_BANNERS=true

Rules:

- API base URL must be configurable.
- Mock fallback must be enabled by default.
- Polling interval must be configurable.
- Dashboard should not crash if API is offline.

============================================================
BACKEND CONFIG UPDATES
============================================================

Update backend `.env.example` if needed:

FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
CORS_ALLOW_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://127.0.0.1:5173

Update backend CORS config in FastAPI:

- Allow frontend dev origin
- Keep production configurable
- Do not allow wildcard credentials in production
- Preserve all existing routes

