============================================================
API CLIENT REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create:

frontend/src/api/client.ts

Requirements:

- Central fetch wrapper
- Handles standard API response shape:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

- Throws typed error for `ok=false`
- Supports GET, POST, DELETE
- Supports timeout
- Supports mock fallback when backend is unavailable
- Does not hardcode API URL

Create:

frontend/src/api/endpoints.ts

